[
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"03541 0559\">spoke</st> about the <st data-num=\"01121 05983\">Ammonites</st>:<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cDo you think <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">there are not</st> any <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">people</st> of the nation of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> remaining?<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">Do you think</st> <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">there are not</st> <st data-num=\"03423\" class=\"\">any</st> of them remaining <st data-num=\"03423\" class=\"\">to reinherit</st> their land?<p class=\"poetry\">Is that <st data-num=\"04069\" class=\"\">why</st> you <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> who worship the god <st data-num=\"04445\" class=\"\">Milcom</st><n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">have <st data-num=\"03423\" class=\"\">taken possession of</st> the territory of <st data-num=\"01410\" class=\"\">Gad</st> and <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">live</st> in his <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">cities</st>?<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03651 02009\">Because you did that</st>, <p class=\"poetry\">I, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">affirm</st> that<n id=\"1\" /> a <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">time</st> is <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">coming</st><p class=\"poetry\">when I will make <st data-num=\"07237\" class=\"\">Rabbah</st>, the capital city of <st data-num=\"01121 05983\">Ammon</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">hear</st> the <st data-num=\"08643\" class=\"\">sound of the</st> <st data-num=\"04421\" class=\"\">battle</st> <st data-num=\"08643\" class=\"\">cry</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">It will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">become</st> a <st data-num=\"08510\" class=\"\">mound</st> covered with <st data-num=\"08077\" class=\"\">ruins</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Its <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">villages</st> will be <st data-num=\"03341\" class=\"\">burned</st> <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">to the ground</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Then <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> will <st data-num=\"03423\" class=\"\">take back</st> its <st data-num=\"03423\" class=\"\">land</st> <p class=\"poetry\">from those who took their land from them.<p class=\"poetry\">I, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">affirm</st> it!<n id=\"4\" /></p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03213\" class=\"\">Wail</st>, you people in <st data-num=\"02809\" class=\"\">Heshbon</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> <st data-num=\"05857\" class=\"\">Ai</st> in Ammon is <st data-num=\"07703\" class=\"\">destroyed</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06817\" class=\"\">Cry out in anguish</st>, you people in the <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">villages</st> surrounding<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"07237\" class=\"\">Rabbah</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02296\" class=\"\">Put on</st> <st data-num=\"08242\" class=\"\">sackcloth</st> and <st data-num=\"05594\" class=\"\">cry out in mourning</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07751\" class=\"\">Run about</st> covered with <st data-num=\"01417\" class=\"\">gashes</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> your god <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">Milcom</st> will <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">go</st> into <st data-num=\"01473\" class=\"\">exile</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03162\" class=\"\">along with</st> his <st data-num=\"03548\" class=\"\">priests</st> and <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">officials</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">Why</st> do you <st data-num=\"01984\" class=\"\">brag</st> about your great power?<p class=\"poetry\">Your power is <st data-num=\"02100\" class=\"\">ebbing away</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> you <st data-num=\"07728\" class=\"\">rebellious</st> <st data-num=\"01323\" class=\"\">people</st> of Ammon,<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">who <st data-num=\"0982\" class=\"\">trust</st> in your <st data-num=\"0214\" class=\"\">riches</st> and say,<p class=\"poetry\">\u2018<st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> would dare to <st data-num=\"0935 0413\">attack</st> us?\u2019</p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">will</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">bring</st> <st data-num=\"06343\" class=\"\">terror</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> you from <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">every</st> <st data-num=\"05439\" class=\"\">side</st>,\u201d<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <st data-num=\"0136\" class=\"\">Sovereign</st> <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cYou will be <st data-num=\"05080\" class=\"\">scattered</st> <st data-num=\"0376 06440\">in every direction</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">No</st> one will <st data-num=\"06908\" class=\"\">gather</st> the <st data-num=\"05074\" class=\"\">fugitives</st> back <st data-num=\"06908\" class=\"\">together</st>.</p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Yet <st data-num=\"0310 03651\">in days to come</st> <p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">reverse</st> <st data-num=\"01121 05983\">Ammon\u2019s</st> ill <st data-num=\"07622\" class=\"\">fortune</st>.\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03541 0559\">spoke</st> about <st data-num=\"0123\" class=\"\">Edom</st>:<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cIs <st data-num=\"02451\" class=\"\">wisdom</st> <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"05750\" class=\"\">longer</st> to be found in <st data-num=\"08487\" class=\"\">Teman</st>?<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06\" class=\"\">Can</st> Edom\u2019s <st data-num=\"0995\" class=\"\">counselors</st> <st data-num=\"06\" class=\"\">not give</st> her any good <st data-num=\"06098\" class=\"\">advice</st>?<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Has all their <st data-num=\"02451\" class=\"\">wisdom</st> turned bad?<n id=\"5\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06437\" class=\"\">Turn</st> and <st data-num=\"05127\" class=\"\">flee</st>! <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">Take up refuge</st> <st data-num=\"06009\" class=\"\">in remote places</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">you people who <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">live</st> in <st data-num=\"01719\" class=\"\">Dedan</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> I will <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">bring</st> <st data-num=\"0343\" class=\"\">disaster</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> the descendants of <st data-num=\"06215\" class=\"\">Esau</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I have decided it is <st data-num=\"06256\" class=\"\">time</st> for me to <st data-num=\"06485\" class=\"\">punish</st> them.<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">If</st> <st data-num=\"01219\" class=\"\">grape pickers</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">came</st> to pick your grapes,<p class=\"poetry\">would they <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07604\" class=\"\">leave</st> <st data-num=\"05955\" class=\"\">a few grapes behind</st>?<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0518\" class=\"\">If</st> <st data-num=\"01590\" class=\"\">robbers</st> came at <st data-num=\"03915\" class=\"\">night</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">would they not <st data-num=\"07843\" class=\"\">pillage</st> only <st data-num=\"01767\" class=\"\">what</st> they <st data-num=\"01767\" class=\"\">needed</st>?<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">But</st> <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> will <st data-num=\"02834\" class=\"\">strip</st> everything <st data-num=\"02834\" class=\"\">away</st> from <st data-num=\"06215\" class=\"\">Esau\u2019s</st> descendants.<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"01540\" class=\"\">uncover</st> their <st data-num=\"04565\" class=\"\">hiding places</st> so they <st data-num=\"03808 03201\">cannot</st> <st data-num=\"02247\" class=\"\">hide</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Their <st data-num=\"02233\" class=\"\">children</st>, <st data-num=\"0251\" class=\"\">relatives</st>, and <st data-num=\"07934\" class=\"\">neighbors</st> will all be <st data-num=\"07703\" class=\"\">destroyed</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">Not</st> one of them <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">will be</st> left!</p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">Leave</st> your <st data-num=\"03490\" class=\"\">orphans</st> <st data-num=\"05800\">behind</st>, and <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> will <st data-num=\"02421\" class=\"\">keep</st> them <st data-num=\"02421\" class=\"\">alive</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Your <st data-num=\"0490\" class=\"\">widows</st>, too, can <st data-num=\"0982\" class=\"\">depend</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> me.\u201d<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"03541 0559\">says</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">If</st> even those <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> did <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">deserve</st> to <st data-num=\"08354\" class=\"\">drink</st> from the <st data-num=\"03563\" class=\"\">cup</st> of my wrath <st data-num=\"08354\" class=\"\">must</st> <st data-num=\"08354\" class=\"\">drink</st> from it, do <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> think <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">you</st> will <st data-num=\"05352\" class=\"\">go</st> <st data-num=\"05352\" class=\"\">unpunished</st>? You will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"05352\" class=\"\">go unpunished</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">but</st> must <st data-num=\"08354\" class=\"\">certainly</st> <st data-num=\"08354\" class=\"\">drink</st> from the cup of my wrath.<n id=\"1\" />",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> I solemnly <st data-num=\"07650\" class=\"\">swear</st>,\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, \u201c<st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"01224\" class=\"\">Bozrah</st><n id=\"2\" /> will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">become</st> a <st data-num=\"02721\" class=\"\">pile of ruins</st>. It will become an <st data-num=\"08047 02781\">object of</st> <st data-num=\"08047\" class=\"\">horror</st> and <st data-num=\"02781\" class=\"\">ridicule</st>, an <st data-num=\"07045\" class=\"\">example to be used in curses</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">towns</st> around it will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">lie</st> in <st data-num=\"02723\" class=\"\">ruins</st> <st data-num=\"05769\" class=\"\">forever</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I said,<n id=\"1\" /> \u201cI have <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st> a <st data-num=\"08052\" class=\"\">message</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">from</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>.<p class=\"poetry\">A <st data-num=\"06735\" class=\"\">messenger</st> has been <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">sent</st> among the <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st> to say,<p class=\"poetry\">\u2018<st data-num=\"06908\" class=\"\">Gather</st> your armies and <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">march out</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">against</st> her!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">Prepare</st> to do <st data-num=\"04421\" class=\"\">battle</st> with her!\u2019\u201d<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span> says to Edom,<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cI <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">will</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">certainly</st> <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">make</st> you <st data-num=\"06996\" class=\"\">small</st> among <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I will make you <st data-num=\"0959\" class=\"\">despised</st> by all <st data-num=\"0120\" class=\"\">humankind</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"08606\" class=\"\">terror</st> you inspire in others<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and the <st data-num=\"02087\" class=\"\">arrogance</st> of your <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">heart</st> have <st data-num=\"05377\" class=\"\">deceived</st> you.<p class=\"poetry\">You may <st data-num=\"07931\" class=\"\">make</st> your <st data-num=\"07931\" class=\"\">home</st> in the <st data-num=\"02288\" class=\"\">clefts</st> of the <st data-num=\"05553\" class=\"\">rocks</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">you may <st data-num=\"08610\" class=\"\">occupy</st> the <st data-num=\"04791\" class=\"\">highest places</st> in the <st data-num=\"01389\" class=\"\">hills</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">But</st> even <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">if</st> you <st data-num=\"01361\" class=\"\">made</st> your <st data-num=\"01361\" class=\"\">home</st> where the <st data-num=\"05404\" class=\"\">eagles</st> <st data-num=\"07064\" class=\"\">nest</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">I would <st data-num=\"03381\" class=\"\">bring</st> you <st data-num=\"03381\" class=\"\">down</st> from <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">there</st>,\u201d<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. </p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"0123\" class=\"\">Edom</st> will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">become</st> an <st data-num=\"08047\" class=\"\">object of horror</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> who <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">pass</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">by</st> it will <st data-num=\"08074\">be filled with horror</st>; <p class=\"poetry\">they will <st data-num=\"08319\" class=\"\">hiss out</st> their <st data-num=\"08319\" class=\"\">scorn</st> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">because of</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"04347\" class=\"\">disasters</st> that have happened to it.<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Edom will be <st data-num=\"04114\" class=\"\">destroyed</st> like <st data-num=\"05467\" class=\"\">Sodom</st> and <st data-num=\"06017\" class=\"\">Gomorrah</st><p class=\"poetry\">and the <st data-num=\"07934\" class=\"\">towns that were around</st> them.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">No</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">one</st> will <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">live</st> <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">there</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">No</st> <st data-num=\"01121 0120\">human being</st> will <st data-num=\"01481\" class=\"\">settle</st> in it,\u201d<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>. </p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cA <st data-num=\"0738\" class=\"\">lion</st> <st data-num=\"02009 05927\">coming up</st> from the <st data-num=\"01347\" class=\"\">thick undergrowth</st> along the <st data-num=\"03383\" class=\"\">Jordan</st><n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">scatters the sheep <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">in</st> the <st data-num=\"05116\" class=\"\">pastureland</st> <st data-num=\"0386\" class=\"\">around it</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">So</st> too I will <st data-num=\"07280 07323\">chase</st> the Edomites <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">off</st> their land.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Then I will <st data-num=\"06485\" class=\"\">appoint</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">over</st> it <st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">whomever</st> I <st data-num=\"0970\" class=\"\">choose</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> there is <st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">no one</st> <st data-num=\"03644\" class=\"\">like</st> <st data-num=\"03644\" class=\"\">me</st>, and there is <st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">no one</st> who can <st data-num=\"03259\" class=\"\">call</st> me <st data-num=\"03259\" class=\"\">to account</st>.<n id=\"5\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">There</st> is <st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">no</st><n id=\"6\" /> <st data-num=\"07462\" class=\"\">ruler</st><n id=\"7\" /> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> can <st data-num=\"05975\" class=\"\">stand up</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">against</st> me. </p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">So</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">listen to</st> <st data-num=\"06098 0834\">what</st> I, the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, have <st data-num=\"03289\" class=\"\">planned</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">against</st> <st data-num=\"0123\" class=\"\">Edom</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04284 0834\">what</st> I <st data-num=\"02803\" class=\"\">intend to do</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st><n id=\"1\" /> the people who <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">live</st> in <st data-num=\"08487\" class=\"\">Teman</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"06629\" class=\"\">Their</st> <st data-num=\"06810\" class=\"\">little ones</st> <st data-num=\"0518 03808\">will</st> be <st data-num=\"05498\" class=\"\">dragged off</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I <st data-num=\"0518 03808\">will</st> <st data-num=\"08074\" class=\"\">completely destroy</st> their <st data-num=\"05116\" class=\"\">land</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">because of</st> what they have done.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The people of the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st> will <st data-num=\"07493\" class=\"\">quake</st> when they <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">hear</st> of their <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">downfall</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Their <st data-num=\"06818 06963\">cries of anguish</st> will be <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st> all the way to the <st data-num=\"03220\" class=\"\">Gulf</st> of <st data-num=\"05488\" class=\"\">Aqaba</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Look</st>! Like an <st data-num=\"05404\" class=\"\">eagle</st> with <st data-num=\"06566\" class=\"\">outspread</st> <st data-num=\"03671\" class=\"\">wings</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">a nation will <st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">soar up</st> and <st data-num=\"01675\" class=\"\">swoop down</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> <st data-num=\"01224\" class=\"\">Bozrah</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">At <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">time</st> the <st data-num=\"01368\" class=\"\">soldiers</st> of <st data-num=\"0123\" class=\"\">Edom</st> will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> as <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">fearful</st> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">as</st> a <st data-num=\"0802\" class=\"\">woman</st> in <st data-num=\"06887\" class=\"\">labor</st>.\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\">Lord</span> spoke<n id=\"1\" /> about <st data-num=\"01834\" class=\"\">Damascus</st>:<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cThe people of <st data-num=\"02574\" class=\"\">Hamath</st> and <st data-num=\"0774\" class=\"\">Arpad</st><n id=\"3\" /> will be <st data-num=\"0954\" class=\"\">dismayed</st><p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> they have <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st> <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">bad</st> <st data-num=\"08052\" class=\"\">news</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Their <st data-num=\"03820\" class=\"\">courage</st> will <st data-num=\"04127\" class=\"\">melt away</st> because of <st data-num=\"01674\" class=\"\">worry</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Their hearts will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03201\" class=\"\">be able</st> to <st data-num=\"08252\" class=\"\">rest</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "23"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The people of <st data-num=\"01834\" class=\"\">Damascus</st> will <st data-num=\"07503\" class=\"\">lose heart</st> and <st data-num=\"06437\" class=\"\">turn</st> to <st data-num=\"05127\" class=\"\">flee</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07374\" class=\"\">Panic</st> will <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">grip</st> them.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02256\" class=\"\">Pain</st> and <st data-num=\"06869\" class=\"\">anguish</st> will <st data-num=\"0270\" class=\"\">seize</st> them<p class=\"poetry\">like a woman <st data-num=\"03205\" class=\"\">in labor</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "24"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0349\">How</st> <st data-num=\"05800\" class=\"\">deserted</st> will that <st data-num=\"08416\" class=\"\">once-famous</st> <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">city</st><n id=\"1\" /> be,<p class=\"poetry\">that <st data-num=\"07151\" class=\"\">city</st> that was once filled with<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"04885\" class=\"\">joy</st>!<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "25"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">For</st> her <st data-num=\"0970\" class=\"\">young men</st> will <st data-num=\"05307\" class=\"\">fall</st> in her <st data-num=\"07339\" class=\"\">city squares</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> her <st data-num=\"0376 04421\">soldiers</st> will be <st data-num=\"01826\" class=\"\">destroyed</st> at <st data-num=\"01931\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">time</st>,\u201d<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "26"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cI will <st data-num=\"03341\" class=\"\">set</st> <st data-num=\"0784\" class=\"\">fire</st> to the <st data-num=\"02346\" class=\"\">walls</st> of <st data-num=\"01834\" class=\"\">Damascus</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">it will <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">burn up</st> the <st data-num=\"0759\" class=\"\">palaces</st> of <st data-num=\"01130\" class=\"\">Ben Hadad</st>.\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "27"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"03541 0559\">spoke</st> about <st data-num=\"06938\" class=\"\">Kedar</st><n id=\"1\" /> and the <st data-num=\"04467\" class=\"\">kingdoms</st> of <st data-num=\"02674\" class=\"\">Hazor</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"05020\" class=\"\">Nebuchadnezzar</st> of <st data-num=\"0894\" class=\"\">Babylon</st> <st data-num=\"05221\" class=\"\">conquered</st>: <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cArmy of Babylon,<n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">go</st> and <st data-num=\"05927 0413\">attack</st> <st data-num=\"06938\" class=\"\">Kedar</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07703\" class=\"\">Lay waste</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">those who live in</st> the <st data-num=\"06924\" class=\"\">eastern desert</st>.<n id=\"4\" /></p>",
    "verse": "28"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Their <st data-num=\"0168\" class=\"\">tents</st> and their <st data-num=\"06629\" class=\"\">flocks</st> will be <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">taken away</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Their <st data-num=\"03407\" class=\"\">tent curtains</st>, <st data-num=\"03605 03627\">equipment</st>, and <st data-num=\"01581\" class=\"\">camels</st> will be <st data-num=\"05375 01992\">carried off</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">People will <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">shout</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to</st> them,<p class=\"poetry\">\u2018<st data-num=\"04032\" class=\"\">Terror</st> is <st data-num=\"05439\" class=\"\">all around</st> you!\u2019\u201d<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "29"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> \u201c<st data-num=\"05127\" class=\"\">Flee</st> <st data-num=\"05110 03966\">quickly</st>, you who <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">live</st> in <st data-num=\"02674\" class=\"\">Hazor</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">Take up refuge</st> <st data-num=\"06009\">in remote places</st>.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"05019\" class=\"\">Nebuchadnezzar</st> of <st data-num=\"0894\" class=\"\">Babylon</st> has <st data-num=\"03289\" class=\"\">laid out</st> <st data-num=\"06098\" class=\"\">plans</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">to attack</st> you.<p class=\"poetry\">He has <st data-num=\"02803\" class=\"\">formed</st> his <st data-num=\"04284\" class=\"\">strategy</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on how to defeat</st> you.\u201d<n id=\"4\" /></p>",
    "verse": "30"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> \u201cArmy of Babylon,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">go</st> and <st data-num=\"05927 0413\">attack</st><p class=\"poetry\">a <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nation</st> that <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">lives</st> in <st data-num=\"07961\" class=\"\">peace</st> and <st data-num=\"0983\" class=\"\">security</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">They have <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">no</st> <st data-num=\"01817\" class=\"\">gates</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"01280\" class=\"\">walls</st> to protect them.<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">They <st data-num=\"07931\" class=\"\">live</st> <st data-num=\"0910\" class=\"\">all alone</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "31"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Their <st data-num=\"01581\" class=\"\">camels</st> will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> taken as <st data-num=\"0957\" class=\"\">plunder</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Their <st data-num=\"01995\" class=\"\">vast</st> <st data-num=\"04735\" class=\"\">herds</st> will be taken as <st data-num=\"07998\" class=\"\">spoil</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"02219\" class=\"\">scatter</st> to the <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">four</st> <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">winds</st><p class=\"poetry\">those desert peoples who <st data-num=\"07112\" class=\"\">cut</st> their hair <st data-num=\"07112\" class=\"\">short</st> at the <st data-num=\"06285\" class=\"\">temples</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">bring</st> <st data-num=\"0343\" class=\"\">disaster</st> against them<p class=\"poetry\">from <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">every</st> <st data-num=\"05676\" class=\"\">direction</st>,\u201d <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "32"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"02674\" class=\"\">Hazor</st> will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">become</st> a <st data-num=\"05704 05769\">permanent</st> <st data-num=\"08077\" class=\"\">wasteland</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">a <st data-num=\"04583\" class=\"\">place where</st> only <st data-num=\"08577\" class=\"\">jackals</st> <st data-num=\"04583\" class=\"\">live</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">No</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">one</st> will <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">live</st> <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">there</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">No</st> <st data-num=\"01121 0120\">human being</st> will <st data-num=\"01481\" class=\"\">settle</st> in it.\u201d<n id=\"2\" /></p>",
    "verse": "33"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">This</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">was</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\">Lord</st></span>\u2019s <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">message</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"05030\" class=\"\">prophet</st> <st data-num=\"03414\" class=\"\">Jeremiah</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">about</st> <st data-num=\"05867\" class=\"\">Elam,</st><n id=\"2\" /> which came <st data-num=\"07225\" class=\"\">early</st> in the <st data-num=\"04438\" class=\"\">reign</st><n id=\"3\" /> of <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"06667\" class=\"\">Zedekiah</st> of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "34"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> of <st data-num=\"06635\">Heaven\u2019s Armies</st> <st data-num=\"03541 0559\">said</st>:<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cI <st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">will</st> <st data-num=\"07665\" class=\"\">kill</st> all the <st data-num=\"07198\" class=\"\">archers</st> of <st data-num=\"05867\" class=\"\">Elam</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">who are the <st data-num=\"07225\" class=\"\">chief source</st> of her <st data-num=\"01369\" class=\"\">military might</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "35"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">cause</st> enemies to blow <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">through</st> <st data-num=\"05867\" class=\"\">Elam</st> from <st data-num=\"0702\" class=\"\">every</st> direction<p class=\"poetry\">like the <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">winds</st> blowing in from the <st data-num=\"0702\" class=\"\">four</st> <st data-num=\"07098\" class=\"\">quarters</st> of <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">heaven</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"02219\" class=\"\">scatter</st> the people of Elam to <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">the</st> <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">four</st> <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">winds</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">There will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> any <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nation</st> <st data-num=\"0834 08033\">where</st> the <st data-num=\"05080\" class=\"\">refugees</st> of <st data-num=\"05867\" class=\"\">Elam</st> will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">go</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "36"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will make the people of <st data-num=\"05867\" class=\"\">Elam</st> <st data-num=\"02865\" class=\"\">terrified</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">of</st> their <st data-num=\"0341\" class=\"\">enemies</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">who are <st data-num=\"01245\" class=\"\">seeking</st> to <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">kill</st> them.<p class=\"poetry\">I will vent my <st data-num=\"02740\" class=\"\">fierce</st> <st data-num=\"0639\" class=\"\">anger</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">bring</st> <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">disaster</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">upon</st> them,\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">\u201cI will <st data-num=\"07971\" class=\"\">send</st> <st data-num=\"02719\" class=\"\">armies</st> chasing <st data-num=\"0310\" class=\"\">after</st> them<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05704\" class=\"\">until</st> I have <st data-num=\"03615\" class=\"\">completely destroyed</st> them. </p>",
    "verse": "37"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"07760\" class=\"\">establish</st> my <st data-num=\"03678\" class=\"\">sovereignty</st> over <st data-num=\"05867\" class=\"\">Elam</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"06\" class=\"\">destroy</st> <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">their</st> <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> and their <st data-num=\"08269\" class=\"\">leaders</st>,\u201d<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>.<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "38"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Jeremiah",
    "chapter": "49",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"> \u201c<st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">Yet</st> in <st data-num=\"0319\">future</st> <st data-num=\"03117\">days</st> <p class=\"poetry\">I will <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">reverse</st> <st data-num=\"05867\" class=\"\">Elam\u2019s</st> ill <st data-num=\"07622\" class=\"\">fortune</st>,\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05002\" class=\"\">says</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>.</p>",
    "verse": "39"
  }
]